==Third round==
{{main|2026 FIFA World Cup qualification – CONCACAF third round}}

In the third round, the twelve teams advancing from the second round were drawn into three groups of four teams to play round-robin home-and-away matches. The three group winners qualified for the World Cup, and the two best-ranked runners-up advanced to the [[2026 FIFA World Cup qualification (inter-confederation play-offs)|inter-confederation play-offs]].<ref name="CONCACAF format"/> The draw for the third round was held on 12 June 2025, 19:00 EDT.<ref>{{cite web |title=Concacaf confirms schedule for region's men's FIFA World Cup Qualifying matches taking place in June |url=https://www.concacaf.com/en/world-cup-qualifying-men/news/concacaf-confirms-schedule-for-region-s-men-s-fifa-world-cup-qualifying-matches-taking-place-in-june/ |website=concacaf.com |date=May 2025 |access-date=1 May 2025}}</ref>

